      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. it looks good, but since our clients are high-net-worth and expect a very specific level of personalized service, maybe we should add a section about the \"concierge experience\"? i'm a bit worried they might feel like the service is becoming more \"automated\" and less \"human\" with the new, faster model. can you write a bit that explains how the new system will handle the complex, nuanced requests you currently manage? maybe highlight some of the subtle things that might be harder for a faster, simpler engine to catch?",
